LRS1.DE.summary: Lakestar SPAC I SE focuses on acquiring a company in the form of a merger, capital stock exchange, share purchase, asset acquisition, reorganization, or similar transaction. It intends acquire companies in the technology sector with a focus on the sub-sectors, such as software as a service, fintech, transportation and logistics, healthtech, and deep tech. The company is based in Luxembourg City, Luxembourg.

SPAC.F.summary: 468 SPAC I SE operates as a special purpose acquisition company. The company intends to acquire operating business with principal business operations in a member state of the European Economic Area or the United Kingdom, or Switzerland in the form of a merger, capital stock exchange, share purchase, asset acquisition, reorganization, or similar transaction. It plans to target a company in the technology and technology-enabled sector with a focus on the sub-sectors marketplaces, direct-to-consumer, and software and artificial intelligence. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Luxembourg, Luxembourg.
